dc_title_s: Municipalities Fond du Lac County, WI 2016
dc_description_s: This data layer represents municipalities for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2016.[The municipal boundary layer depicts municipal boundaries in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download [During the year approximate annexation updates are entered as received. At the end of each year these annexation boundaries are adjusted for coincidence with parcel data.]
